title: Scrapheap Challenge - The Scrappy Races 2 - 3 - Hill Climb.avi
description:
Hosts : Robert Llewellyn & Lisa Rogers.

The four teams, "The Knuckleheadz", "The Cops 'N' Bodgers", "The Tartan Starlets" and "The Chaos Crew", drive from Rockingham Castle in Northamptonshire to Yorkshire, where they face a steep uphill challenge.

Help me seed (to a ratio of at least 1.5) & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. 

The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

It's a team effort. So please, do your part.
